{"tid":146904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿SIR做嘢跌落坑渠　膝頭受傷送院","createTime":"2017-03-07T13:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T17:49:16.000Z","uid":26769,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"298d2e696b76d4efee5e1fa55cd47d8ab291e2d5","tid":146904,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/457909/xlarge/a7a77971956467090699cf628576adbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F457909%2Fxlarge%2Fa7a77971956467090699cf628576adbf.jpg&h=67de0fac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深井深慈街有坑渠蓋疑損毀（雪糕桶位置），有警員執勤時不慎叉錯腳跌傷送院。（潘安奇攝）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/article/76370\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F76370&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=e3517ef2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/article/76370</a><br />\n<br />\n「飛哥跌落坑渠，飛女睇見流淚 &hellip;&hellip;」是已故名藝人鄧寄塵的經典諧歌的歌詞，豈料今竟發生警生跌落坑渠事件！晚上7時36分，一名警員正於深井嘉頓麵包廠對開執勤期間，懷疑路上坑渠蓋有損毀露出大缺口，警員不慎「叉錯腳」，失足跌落坑渠，膝頭擦傷需送院治理。"},{"pid":"ddad1f79873665f31e3e37af1f8d6aacec1ff58f","tid":146904,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a9c8f7c057fcc0e96be42be158c86f2139ed80","tid":146904,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:07:44.000Z","msg":"呀SIR 仆街唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16cd0572f14301d5f972f1372de32b4af4f6d8b","tid":146904,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:10:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呀SIR 仆街唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能阿SIR係肥仔<img src=\"/as